data.description: If you are looking for small town living that still has amenities, then this is your chance to own a 4 bedroom house in Hankinson. The home has hardwood floors, formal dining room, large living room and 2 baths. There is a full bath and 1 bedroom on the main floor, and 3 bedrooms upstairs with a bonus 4 seasons porch. Large corner lot and a 1 stall detached garage that was converted into a workspace/office. Seller used wood burner attached to ductwork. Conventional financing is best.
